          "fill": "#71717A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Emdy as a Braun product — honest materials, no decoration, everything in service of function. The app is a reading instrument, not a reading environment. The website reflects this: technical confidence, restrained palette, information delivered with the density and clarity of a product spec sheet. The icon is a geometric mark — reduced, precise, immediately recognizable at 16px.",
