          "fill": "#71717A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Single-page product site. Hero: app screenshot on #F0F2F5, one headline in Plex Sans Semibold, one subline. Feature grid below — 3×2, each cell is an icon + label + one sentence. No animations, no parallax, no testimonials. Footer: download link, version number, GitHub. The page loads fast and says everything in the viewport.",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
          "fontSize": 14
