          "name": "wd2",
          "fill": "#71717A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Editorial single-page. Generous vertical rhythm — 80px+ between sections. Large serif headline, a single paragraph of body copy, then an app screenshot floating on warm white. Features presented as short prose paragraphs rather than a grid. Feels like the About page of a small press. Download button is understated — a text link with an arrow, not a shouting CTA.",
