          "fill": "#71717A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Emdy through the lens of typographic craft — the app as a compositor's proof, the website as a specimen sheet. High contrast, sharp details, the confidence of ink on good paper. This direction leans into the typography itself as the design element. The icon is a ligature or typographic detail that signals expertise and care.",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
