          "name": "wl3",
          "fill": "#999999",
          "content": "WEBSITE DIRECTION",
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "500",
          "letterSpacing": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "hDaLO",
          "name": "wd3",
          "fill": "#71717A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Type specimen meets product page. The hero is a massive serif headline — 'Emdy' set at 120px+ — with a single sentence underneath. The app screenshot sits in a high-contrast frame (dark mode on white, or light mode on black). Feature descriptions use the serif/sans pairing to create editorial rhythm. A thin red rule separates sections. The footer feels like a colophon: version, typefaces used, build date.",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
          "fontSize": 14
        },
