          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "The quiet confidence of good steel.",
          "lineHeight": 1.2,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Sans",
          "fontSize": 36,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "vNepf",
          "name": "p4",
          "fill": "#7A7268",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Slate blue as the soul of the product — the color of brushed aluminum panels on a Braun hi-fi, of overcast sky through a factory window, of the system itself receding so content can advance. This direction grounds Emdy in industrial calm. The website feels like a product data sheet from a company that trusts its engineering. The icon carries the blue as a quiet signature.",
