              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "The monogram in slate blue — like a maker's mark stamped into aluminum. Three variants: light field (cool wash bg), dark field (deep slate bg), and solid (slate blue bg with white mark). The medium-weight sans-serif 'M' reads as engineering, not design.",
