          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Cool-toned product page with warm undertones. Hero section: app screenshot on #ECF0F2, headline in Plex Sans Medium, a single line of slate-blue metadata underneath (v1.0 · macOS · 2.1 MB). Features in a two-column layout with Plex Mono labels in #5A6D7A and Plex Sans descriptions in charcoal. Dark mode section flips to #3A4A52 background with #B0C0C8 text. The page has the calm authority of a Braun product manual.",
